{"type": "article", "id": 25373, "title": "背景是雅典城的音乐专辑", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-13T07:14:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607101140AvGHeI0oF6KjwWrY.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盘专辑是为一个名叫 The Voodootricks 的音乐团队设计的，他们擅长 rap，音乐灵感来自希腊当地的文化。专辑的封面则强调了这种联系，最外一层的黑色盒子带有镂空的乐队的名字，而下面蓝色的图像是雅典城，重叠在一起时可以隐约看到建筑的背景。黑色的专辑色调搭配亮丽的蓝色可以展示出独特和这种异域风格。设计师是来自希腊的 90 后，<a href=\"http://www.adamantiachatzivasileiou.com/Work-1/The-Voodootricks-Album-cover\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101138exY0TgjLImRZwP9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.50833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071011387oAT3rwcVal80RMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101138W1z5kBZCjKy94Ugi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101139p24sdcqvA1SN7fRW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071011390SoHLE8bUimpXWuY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}